<br>
So, last night I moved to Qinimi.  The Nocs seem pretty easy, and I similarly chant kited the deathhounds/fleshhounds without much difficulty (at 112 MR, Ukuns chains was almost always resisted).  I tried one of the huge mobs outside of the bubble (which I understand contains a raid-level encounter) but was dismayed to find that it summoned.  <br>
<br>
I'll be back later tonight to try mobs throughout the rest of the zone, but thought I would take this opportunity to ask what your own experiences have been with soloing as a bard in GoD (beyond Natimbi).  Are summoning mobs the norm or the exception?  Have you found any wide open areas to chant in outside of the entrance from Natimbi?  My very brief experiences with other zones (Barindu and an expedition) seemed to indicate that those zones were packed with mobs, making chant kiting singles very difficult.<br>
<br>
I don't believe any of this information cold be described as pertinent to guild-advancement in GoD, so I don't think I am stepping on any toes by asking for some general data. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   As I continue to try to make my own way, I'll certainly be happy to fill in this post with my own data -- the info on Allakhazams is less than helpful so far. <p>&quot;Classes are not that out of balance&quot; -AbsorEQ</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub147.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sevlor>Sevlor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 237<br> <font color=#330000>(3/22/04 2:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallontour.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=314.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://mywebpages.comcast.net/sevlor/images/SevlorCartoon.gif width=106 height=168></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Soloing in GoD</span><hr size=1> Riwwi rocks for charm kiting <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
